dc_title_s: Commission of Fine Arts Review Area: Washington, D.C.
dc_description_s: Commission of fine arts review areas. The dataset contains locations and attributes of CFA review areasC. Office of the Chief Technology Officer (OCTO) and participating D.C. government agencies. All DC GIS data is stored and exported in Maryland State Plane coordinates NAD 83 meters. This layer captured all squares that bounded the Shipstead-Luce boundary. For the areas within this jurisdiction boundary and outside the Shipstead-Luce boundary METADATA CONTENT IS IN PROCESS OF VALIDATION AND SUBJECT TO CHANGE.
